{"tid":455544,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"有咩方法可以忘記一個人","createTime":"2017-11-02T07:42:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-03T02:45:07.000Z","uid":130574,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"d74d027aed6c4dc1101ac35d71119442b2f27f53","tid":455544,"uid":130574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:42:44.000Z","msg":"日日諗佢真係好辛苦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n個心好痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff2b80f7f9fab1f2555bf216be1dd0f4a5d9400f","tid":455544,"uid":94533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:46:40.000Z","msg":"時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b5556d5a521859350be09279f2fbb42f6c55df5","tid":455544,"uid":34680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:48:40.000Z","msg":"冇"},{"pid":"983a12877477ded582b2a473c99ade7e9de877d9","tid":455544,"uid":130574,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:49:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>時間<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/want_die.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a810fc418ed7f101193f9c271cd512ac5d0e64ad","tid":455544,"uid":12360,"like":3,"dislike":3,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:51:31.000Z","msg":"個個都答時間 你估個個都想答時間咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb87567b1fe8edea418d75dc416ee4cef4fdd833","tid":455544,"uid":140630,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:54:16.000Z","msg":"其實你諗通左 就可以好快放低"},{"pid":"386caa9e8e088b23d4cd5f7cf0c6326ffb49a707","tid":455544,"uid":130574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T07:54:18.000Z","msg":"佢一次機會都唔肯比我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  <br />\n點解要咁"},{"pid":"2